{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-js","path":"/project/laravel-user-role-scaffold","webpackCompilationHash":"88fa124b58fd1c2c9eae","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"94936b90-70ad-5cc6-9b00-02801eb873c3","html":"<p><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/dcyar/laravel-user-role-scaffold\" target=\"_blank\">Laravel User-Role Scaffold</a></strong> es un proyecto base para cualquier proyecto que requiera el uso de roles de usuario.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1280px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6bf009a989e6e5d8cd4983875e154efb/6e116/dashboard.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.63541666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"OREC-EX Dashboard\"\n        title=\"OREC-EX Dashboard\"\n        src=\"/static/6bf009a989e6e5d8cd4983875e154efb/bb18b/dashboard.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6bf009a989e6e5d8cd4983875e154efb/5543b/dashboard.png 320w,\n/static/6bf009a989e6e5d8cd4983875e154efb/4b15d/dashboard.png 640w,\n/static/6bf009a989e6e5d8cd4983875e154efb/bb18b/dashboard.png 1280w,\n/static/6bf009a989e6e5d8cd4983875e154efb/6e116/dashboard.png 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br />\n<blockquote>\n<p>Puedes ver mas en el repositorio del proyecto: <a href=\"https://github.com/dcyar/laravel-user-role-scaffold\" target=\"_blank\">Laravel User-Role Scaffold</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Caracteristicas del Sistema:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Roles de usuarios.</li>\n<li>Middleware en rutas.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\">// use middleware on a route\nRoute::get('/users', function () {\n  // do anything\n})->middleware('role:admin');\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>Directivas en blade.</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\">// You can use the scope of the User model\n@if(Auth::user()->hasRole('admin'))\n    // \n@endif\n\n// You can also use the blade directive\n@role('admin')\n    // \n@endrole\n</code></pre>\n<br />\n<blockquote>\n<p>Puedes ver mas en el repositorio del proyecto: <a href=\"https://github.com/dcyar/laravel-user-role-scaffold\" target=\"_blank\">Laravel User-Role Scaffold</a></p>\n</blockquote>","fields":{"slug":"laravel-user-role-scaffold"},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-12-08T00:00:00.000Z","title":"Laravel User-Role Scaffold","tags":["open source","laravel"],"path":"/laravel-user-role-scaffold","description":"Laravel User-Role Scaffold es un proyecto base con la funcionalidad de roles de usuarios..","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":150,"height":150,"src":"/static/201c8b946c162485b438d2ba58f1cd0c/4148e/laravel.png","srcSet":"/static/201c8b946c162485b438d2ba58f1cd0c/4148e/laravel.png 1x"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"laravel-user-role-scaffold"}}}